\fs36  The Game Menu
\fs24 \
 \
There are only two commands enabled in this menu in this version.\
 \

\b New Game...
\b0 :  Starts a new game.  If a game is already in progress you are warned that it will be discarded for the new game.  The Game Setup panel comes up and lets you choose the initial options for the new game.\

\b Change Setup...
\b0 :  Allows you to change the colors and names of the players.  The Game Setup panel has most of its controls disabled.  You can only change the colors and names of the players.\
